<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Golden Grill | Culinary Excellence</title>
    <style>
        :root {
            --black: #050505;
            --dark: #121212;
            --gold: #D4AF37;
            --text: #f0f0f0;
        }

        * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
        body { background: var(--black); color: var(--text); font-family: 'Garamond', serif; overflow-x: hidden; }

        /* NAVIGATION BAR */
        nav {
            background: rgba(5, 5, 5, 0.98);
            border-bottom: 1px solid #222;
            padding: 1.2rem 5%;
            position: fixed; width: 100%; top: 0; z-index: 1000;
            display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center;
        }
        .logo { color: var(--gold); font-size: 1.8rem; font-weight: bold; text-decoration: none; letter-spacing: 3px; cursor: pointer; }
        .nav-links a {
            color: var(--text); text-decoration: none; margin-left: 30px;
            text-transform: uppercase; font-size: 0.85rem; letter-spacing: 1px; transition: 0.3s; cursor: pointer;
        }
        .nav-links a:hover { color: var(--gold); }

        /* PAGE DISPLAY ENGINE */
        .page { display: none; min-height: 100vh; width: 100%; padding-top: 80px; }
        .active { display: block; animation: fadeIn 0.4s ease-in-out; }
        @keyframes fadeIn { from { opacity: 0; } to { opacity: 1; } }

        /* 1. HOME VIEW */
        #home-view {
            background: linear-gradient(rgba(0,0,0,0.8), rgba(0,0,0,0.8)), 
                        url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1514362545857-3bc16c4c7d1b?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1600&q=80');
            background-size: cover; background-position: center;
            display: none; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; align-items: center; text-align: center;
            padding-top: 0;
        }
        #home-view.active { display: flex; }
        .hero-title { color: var(--gold); font-size: clamp(3rem, 10vw, 6rem); letter-spacing: 15px; margin: 0; }

        /* 2. MENU VIEW (FOLDER SYSTEM) */
        .container { max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 40px 20px; }
        .folder-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(240px, 1fr)); gap: 20px; }
        .folder {
            background: var(--dark); border: 1px solid #222; padding: 60px 20px;
            text-align: center; cursor: pointer; border-top: 4px solid var(--gold); transition: 0.3s;
        }
        .folder:hover { transform: translateY(-8px); border-color: var(--gold); background: #1a1a1a; }
        .folder h3 { color: var(--gold); letter-spacing: 2px; text-transform: uppercase; }

        /* MENU CONTENT DISPLAY */
        #cuisine-items-view { display: none; }
        .back-btn { color: var(--gold); cursor: pointer; margin-bottom: 25px; display: inline-block; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--gold); }
        .menu-cat { color: var(--gold); border-bottom: 1px solid #333; margin: 30px 0 10px; padding-bottom: 5px; font-size: 1.4rem; }
        .menu-row { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; padding: 10px 0; border-bottom: 1px dotted #333; }
        .price { color: var(--gold); font-weight: bold; }

        /* 3. BOOKING VIEW */
        .form-card { background: var(--dark); padding: 40px; border: 1px solid var(--gold); max-width: 500px; margin: 40px auto; }
        .form-card input { 
            width: 100%; padding: 12px; margin: 10px 0; background: #000; border: 1px solid #333; color: white; border-radius: 4px;
        }
        .submit-btn { width: 100%; padding: 15px; background: var(--gold); border: none; font-weight: bold; cursor: pointer; color: black; margin-top: 10px;}

        /* 4. REVIEWS VIEW */
        .review-card { background: var(--dark); padding: 30px; margin-bottom: 25px; border-left: 5px solid var(--gold); }
        .stars { color: #FFD700; margin-bottom: 10px; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <nav>
        <div class="logo" onclick="showPage('home-view')">GOLDEN GRILL</div>
        <div class="nav-links">
            <a onclick="showPage('home-view')">Home</a>
            <a onclick="showPage('menu-view')">Menu</a>
            <a onclick="showPage('book-view')">Book a Table</a>
            <a onclick="showPage('review-view')">Review</a>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <div id="home-view" class="page active">
        <h1 class="hero-title">GOLDEN GRILL</h1>
        <p style="letter-spacing: 5px; margin-top: 20px;">A SYMPHONY OF FLAVORS</p>
    </div>

    <div id="menu-view" class="page">
        <div class="container">
            <div id="cuisine-folder-view">
                <h2 style="text-align: center; color: var(--gold); margin-bottom: 40px; letter-spacing: 5px;">WORLD CUISINES</h2>
                <div class="folder-grid">
                    <div class="folder" onclick="openCuisine('Indian')"><h3>Indian</h3></div>
                    <div class="folder" onclick="openCuisine('Italian')"><h3>Italian</h3></div>
                    <div class="folder" onclick="openCuisine('Nepali')"><h3>Nepali</h3></div>
                    <div class="folder" onclick="openCuisine('American')"><h3>American</h3></div>
                    <div class="folder" onclick="openCuisine('Korean')"><h3>Korean</h3></div>
                    <div class="folder" onclick="openCuisine('Japanese')"><h3>Japanese</h3></div>
                    <div class="folder" onclick="openCuisine('Chinese')"><h3>Chinese</h3></div>
                    <div class="folder" onclick="openCuisine('French')"><h3>French</h3></div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div id="cuisine-items-view">
                <div class="back-btn" onclick="backToFolders()">← BACK TO CUISINES</div>
                <h2 id="current-cuisine-title" style="color: var(--gold); font-size: 2.5rem; text-transform: uppercase;"></h2>
                <div id="menu-content-target"></div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div id="book-view" class="page">
        <div class="container">
            <h2 style="text-align: center; color: var(--gold); letter-spacing: 3px;">RESERVE A TABLE</h2>
            <div class="form-card">
                <form onsubmit="alert('Reservation Submitted! We will contact you shortly.'); showPage('home-view'); return false;">
                    <input type="number" placeholder="Number of Members" required>
                    <input type="tel" placeholder="Contact Number" required>
                    <input type="email" placeholder="Email Address" required>
                    <input type="time" required>
                    <button type="submit" class="submit-btn">CONFIRM BOOKING</button>
                </form>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div id="review-view" class="page">
        <div class="container">
            <h2 style="text-align: center; color: var(--gold); margin-bottom: 40px; letter-spacing: 3px;">GUEST REVIEWS</h2>
            <div class="review-card">
                <div class="stars">★★★★★</div>
                <p>"Exceptional Indian cuisine. The Biryani is legendary!"</p>
                <small style="color: var(--gold); font-weight: bold;">- Rohan Mehta</small>
            </div>
            <div class="review-card">
                <div class="stars">★★★★★</div>
                <p>"Best Nepali Momo in the city. The Thakali set is truly authentic."</p>
                <small style="color: var(--gold); font-weight: bold;">- Srijana K.</small>
            </div>
            <div class="review-card">
                <div class="stars">★★★★★</div>
                <p>"The French Onion Soup and wine selection are world-class."</p>
                <small style="color: var(--gold); font-weight: bold;">- Julian D.</small>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

